edu.ucla.sspace.vector

Class MaskedSparseDoubleVectorView

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucla.sspace.vector.MaskedDoubleVectorView
      • edu.ucla.sspace.vector.MaskedSparseDoubleVectorView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DoubleVector, SparseDoubleVector, SparseVector<Double>, Vector<Double>, Serializable

    public class MaskedSparseDoubleVectorView
extends MaskedDoubleVectorView
implements SparseDoubleVector
    A decorator that masked view of a SparseVector through the use of a mapping from new column indices to original column indices. The size of the new vector is based on the number of valid mappings.
    Author:
    Keith Stevens
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
